data.description: Welcome to 513 Middleshare Drive – an impressive 7-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence that defines spacious and comfortable living. This two-story home is thoughtfully designed with a fully finished basement, featuring a separate entrance that could effortlessly transform into a second living quarters or an in-law suite. Step inside to discover a home free of carpets, offering a clean and timeless aesthetic throughout. The flexible layout includes a dedicated office or craft room, a convenient breakfast area, and a formal dining room for special occasions as well as a huge bonus room that is perfect for anything. The heart of the home is the great room, with a striking 2-story ceiling that adds a touch of grandeur. The well-equipped kitchen features stainless steel appliances, ensuring both style and functionality. Recent upgrades include a roof, appliances, and hot water heater, all less than 5 years old – providing peace of mind for years to come. Outside, enjoy a fantastic backyard and the benefits of a vibrant community with access to a pool, clubhouse, playground, and other amenities. This residence at 513 Middleshare Drive offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style, making it a truly exceptional place to call home.
